    "To avoid both proliferating running times and cluttered plots, we uniformly subsampled 20,000 biomolecular structures (Fig. 1).",
    "Total running time for MCES computations was about 15.5 days on a 40 core processor.",
    "To monitor the effect of subsampling, we uniformly subsubsampled nine times 10,000 molecular structures from this set.",
    "We present corresponding UMAP embeddings in Fig. 2, to reveal variations.",
    "We observe that subsampling may indeed change the general layout of the UMAP embedding, but that the general layout is often surprisingly similar."
  ],
